text: Jens Schuermans (born 13 February 1993) is a Belgian mountain bike racer. He rode at the cross-country event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. He was on the start list for the 2018 Cross-country European Championship and he finished. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Belgium Category:People from Genk Category:Sportspeople from Limburg (Belgium)
